      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Active Directory (Azure AD) simplifies authentication for developers by providing identity as a service, with support for industry-standard protocols such as OAuth 2.0 and OpenID Connect, as well as open source libraries for different platforms to help you start coding quickly.",
      "pos": [
        531,
        815
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This document will help you understand the various scenarios Azure AD supports and will show you how to get started.",
      "pos": [
        816,
        932
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It’s divided into the following sections:",
