      "pos": [
        5891,
        5925
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Security tokens issued by Azure AD contain claims, or assertions of information about the subject that has been authenticated.",
      "pos": [
        5927,
        6053
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "These claims can be used by the application for various tasks.",
      "pos": [
        6054,
        6116
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, they can be used to validate the token, identify the subject's directory tenant, display user information, determine the subject's authorization, and so on.",
      "pos": [
